and fetal pigs there are very few people who have lived the kind 
of life miss mccool has lived and we feel this is a sincere 
religious belief jordan said 
even with the recalculation miss mccool figures her d grade 
will only be boosted to a c 
science is not her strong suit ms sweetser said 
