kingsize success at every penney store the somber british tones 
and heavy woolens didnt play well in parts of the south for 
instance 
the indian promotion held in 1988 was considered highly 
successful by the retailer with sales from it approaching 100 
million it was featured in virtually every penney store whereas 
the earlier british and italian ones werent in all the smaller 
stores and the catalogue 
