here are some tips for doityourselfers in the homeselling 
market according to jr paine author of the 30 day way to sell 
your home 
begin by making a checklist of all critical areas of your home 
starting with the front yard eyeing areas that need repair 
dress up your home a house with a neglected appearance 
loudly tells the prospective buyers that its owners do not like it 
do not want it and do not think it has any value or worth 
get a reliable appraisal of your homes true value 
select the best time to market your home as a rule warm 
weather is more conducive to home sales in cold climates and cold 
weather is more conducive in home sales in warm climates 
get a for sale sign 
select a real estate attorney 
select a title company to do your title work 
contact a local lender to obtain current interest rates 
use actioninspiring advertising expressions emphasizing 
money appeal with words like economical bargain or 
value or ego appeal with words like elegant graceful 
or fashionable a homeowner might describe negative attributes 
like a dirt road as a low traffic street safe for children and 
pets or rundown property as a handymans dream 
